name: mercantile
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.1" %}

package:
  name: mercantile
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/m/mercantile/mercantile-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fa3c6db15daffd58454ac198b31887519a19caccee3f9d63d17ae7ff61b3b56b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  entry_points:
    - mercantile=mercantile.scripts:cli

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools
    - click >=3.0

test:
  imports:
    - mercantile
    - mercantile.scripts
  commands:
    - mercantile --help
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/sgillies/mercantile
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Spherical mercator and XYZ tile utilities
  license_family: BSD

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
